Rating: 4
This salad is attractive, fast, easy, and most important ... delicious! I felt that the cayenne flavor (I used a little over 1/4 teaspoon) was too prominent, so I'll cut it back to 1/8 teaspoon the next time I make this salad. The two-serving size of the recipe is very convenient for small families. I highly recommend this salad, and will be making it over and over again!

